summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 80E, page 188 of the Official Land Use Map and Plan 305E, page 190 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone property located at 9600 Martin Luther King, Jr. Way South from Single Family 9600 and Single Family 7200 to Commercial 2/65'; and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Frank Coluccio Construction Company, C.F. 302586 Appl. 9802309)
